It is so easy to make a virgin passion mojito in the comfort of your home. Passion fruit is an excellent source of vitamins, especially vitamin C and A. It is also rich in anti-oxidants and does help a lot in collagen making. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Cut each passion fruit in half and then strain the juice. The seeds should remain in the strainer. Step 2 In a cocktail shaker, muddle the mint leaves and brown sugar. Then add the lime juice to the shaker. Step 3 Fill the shaker with ice, cover and shake vigorously for about 20 seconds. Step 4 Put ice to four glasses and strain the lime mix into each glass. Step 5 Pour the passion fruit juice into each glass, filling the glasses about ¾ of the way to the top. Top the drink with the club soda. Step 6 Float a few of the reserved passion fruit seeds in each glass then enjoy!